reviewText:
If only the vavoooooooom Rochelle Swanson had gotten nekkid this would have been perfect.

It's a very good B movie with action and laughs.  This was when Fred Olen Ray was in his B movie prime and he, Jim Wynorski, and Andy Sidaris made this Heaven on earth for guys who loved hot big jugged babes, action, and good humor.

Top marks for the Pleasure Bots, especially the cutesy pie Lorissa McComas (RIP).

It's a crime against humanity this is not on DVD.
